ZH: 母鸡在雨中找虫子吃。
EN: The hen is looking for worms to eat in the rain.

ZH: 这只母鸡每天早晨都会下蛋。
EN: This hen lays eggs every morning.

ZH: 母鸡正在保护她的小鸡。
EN: The hen is protecting her chicks.

ZH: 这只母鸡已经有十只小鸡了。
EN: This hen already has ten chicks.

ZH: 母鸡在小屋前晒太阳。
EN: The hen is sunbathing in front of the coop.

ZH: 母鸡在鸡舍里筑巢。
EN: The hen is building a nest in the chicken coop.

ZH: 这只母鸡骄傲地大步走。
EN: This hen proudly walks with big steps.

ZH: 母鸡用羽毛把蛋盖住。
EN: The hen covers the eggs with feathers.

ZH: 母鸡在傍晚时分回鸡舍。
EN: The hen returns to the coop in the evening.

ZH: 母鸡在阳光下慢慢长大。
EN: The hen grows slowly in the sunlight.

ZH: 这只母鸡非常勤劳，每天都下蛋。
EN: This hen is very hardworking, laying eggs every day.

ZH: 母鸡用翅膀遮挡小鸡免受风雨之苦。
EN: The hen uses her wings to shield the chicks from the rain.

ZH: 母鸡在农场里自由觅食。
EN: The hen freely forages on the farm.

ZH: 她养了一大群母鸡来产蛋。
EN: She raises a large group of hens for egg production.

ZH: 母鸡会用警惕的眼神盯着周围环境。
EN: The hen will keep a watchful eye on the surroundings.

ZH: 母鸡会给小鸡们讲故事。
EN: The hen tells stories to her chicks.

ZH: 母鸡在绿色的农田里漫步。
EN: The hen strolls in the green fields.

ZH: 母鸡用沙子沐浴来保持清洁。
EN: The hen bathes in sand to stay clean.

ZH: 这只母鸡是他最爱的宠物。
EN: This hen is his favorite pet.
